articles.description: Some additional details about the website
articles.contents:
About Me
Hi! My name is Austin Zhuang, and I go to The
Haverford School.
About the Project
I chose to analyze how financial factors affect access to mental
health using data from IPUMS Health Surveys.
Goals
Visualize data on factors that affect mental health
Creating the correct labels that tell the clearest story

Use visualizations to promote mental health awareness
“This is data science”

Preceptor

Kane’s Free High School
Data Science bootcamp
Github
Repository
